data.description: Pristine one-story home on over half an acre!! This house has been meticulously cared for, with an immense number of upgrades. Drive up the HUGE driveway with tons of parking options to see the beautiful curb appeal including the stone/brick exterior and manicured landscaping. The interior features an open floor plan with high ceilings, hardwood flooring, a split master and much more. Spacious island kitchen bodes a five-burner gas stove top, built-in stainless-steel appliances, bar seating, farm style sink, and tons of cabinet space. The master suite highlights vaulted ceilings, relaxing garden tub, a stand-alone shower, large walk-in closet, double vanity, and sizable linen closet. Command station located off the kitchen is perfect for a second office space. Great sized secondary bedrooms that all come with walk-in closets. The enclosed back patio w/ a wood slatted ceiling and the magnificent, tiered yard is an entertainer's dream! Exquisite built-in grill with granite counters and a sink makes hosting guests seamless. Watch the sunset from the upper tier and enjoy the amazing VIEWS. The yard comes equipped with an extensive drainage system, flagstone walkways, and separate 15by15 concrete pad, that is ready for a second outdoor living space. Tons of room for a pool, sports court, or a multitude of options! Be sure to check out the panoramic VIEW from the top of the backyard. New LG washer and dryer convey. Upgraded water softener system. Garage is equipped with epoxy floors, overhead storage racks, and custom privacy screen to bring the cool breeze in. 30ft extended driveway with a 7ft Iron gate. Full security system includes cameras, windows, doors, motion/break sensors and keypads to convey. Dual GAS water heaters, low annual HOA fees, and a large custom backyard. The six masonry columns along the fence are owned by the seller. Come check out this country living home!
